WEBVTT

00:01.566 --> 00:03.742
Previously onHawaii Five-O:This is a setup.

00:03.786 --> 00:05.396
I mean, you guys
get an anonymous tip, then you

00:05.440 --> 00:06.919
pull Adam over,
and you find a dead body

00:06.963 --> 00:08.225
in the trunk of his car?

00:08.269 --> 00:09.705
It's not just any
dead body.

00:09.748 --> 00:10.880
It's Hideki Tashiro.

00:10.923 --> 00:12.577
ADAM:
My task force
was committed

00:12.621 --> 00:14.057
to finding the person
who murdered

00:14.101 --> 00:15.058
Agent Fischer and his family.

00:15.102 --> 00:16.494
My intel suggested that it

00:16.538 --> 00:18.714
wasn't Hideki;
it was someone above him.

00:18.757 --> 00:20.237
A new player
pulling the strings.

00:20.281 --> 00:21.717
Who?

00:21.760 --> 00:23.153
I don't know yet.

00:23.197 --> 00:25.242
When the M.E. was
conducting the autopsy

00:25.286 --> 00:28.419
on Hideki's body, they
found some foreign DNA,

00:28.463 --> 00:31.640
and it did turn up a
familial match-- to you.

00:31.683 --> 00:34.251
We also know the sample
came from a female.

00:34.295 --> 00:35.992
Adam, you understand what
all this means, right?

00:36.036 --> 00:37.428
I have a half-sister.

00:37.472 --> 00:39.169
And somehow she's involved

00:39.213 --> 00:40.997
in everything that's
been going on.

